{
  "stem": "22652.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I-- they wanted to be alone a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then I went back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then there was whistle blow, [SOBBING] and we were parted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And-- and I remember my mother [CRYING] and myself hanging on to my father and every family just hanging on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they had to tear us away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[SOBBING] And it was the last time I saw my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Now, it-- shortly afterwards, my mother received a letter-- a card-- in German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "She read it to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "My mother knew German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And it was from the Commander [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And it said, your husband has been transferred.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Expect to hear from him soon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we never heard from him again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I just want to mention also, she received a postcard from my father's mother, who was in Poland at the time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And the postcard was written in Spanish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we both cried-- it was written in Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we both cried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And the postcard said, we are suffering so much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We are hungry all the time, and we're cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we don't know [SOBBING] what the future will hold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And we, my mother and I cried, when we got that postcard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we never heard from her again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think, at the beginning of the-- at the outbreak of war, people were kind of running all over the place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'd pack a suitcase and maybe go in the free zone, or-- they were running.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember my mother packing a suitcase for her and for me, and we were in the subway station.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, well, mother, where are we running to?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she says, I don't know, I'm just running away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, well, what's the point?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so, she says, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
